    <title>algorithm</title>
    <link href="/2023/03/07/algorithm/"/>
    <url>/2023/03/07/algorithm/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3 id=""><a href="#" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h3><h3 id="-1"><a href="#-1" class="headerlink" title=""></a></h3><h3 id="动态规划"><a href="#动态规划" class="headerlink" title="动态规划"></a>动态规划</h3><h4 id="70-爬梯子"><a href="#70-爬梯子" class="headerlink" title="70.爬梯子"></a><strong>70.<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/climbing-stairs/">爬梯子</a></strong></h4><p>思路：这个算法的思想是将我们的函数过程理解成到达每一步台阶可以实现的情况。一开始我们是从0级台阶开始向上爬。所以从0级到达1级台阶的方法就只有一种方式。相同的思路从0级台阶到达2级台阶会有2种情况可以实现。而之后，每一级台阶可以由&#x3D;&#x3D;f (i - 1) + f (i - 2)&#x3D;&#x3D;实现。所以我们可以写出递推表达式。</p><hr><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">climbStairs</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> ans[<span class="hljs-number">46</span>];<span class="hljs-comment">//题目要求说n的个数少于45</span><br>        ans[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//到达第一级台阶的方案数</span><br>        ans[<span class="hljs-number">2</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">2</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//同理</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i =<span class="hljs-number">3</span>;i&lt;=<span class="hljs-number">45</span>;i++)&#123;<br>            ans[i] = ans[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>] + ans[i<span class="hljs-number">-2</span>] ;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> ans[n];<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h4 id="类似题目："><a href="#类似题目：" class="headerlink" title="类似题目："></a>类似题目：</h4><p><strong>198.<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/house-robber">打家劫舍</a></strong></p><p>思路：因为不能够连续偷相邻的两家。所以，在偷这一家时，我们要考虑要不要偷，即偷这一家的好处和不偷这一家的好处哪一个更大。</p><hr><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">rob</span><span class="hljs-params">(vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt;&amp; nums)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> sz = nums.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>();<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(sz == <span class="hljs-number">0</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//没有人家</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(sz == <span class="hljs-number">1</span>) <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> nums[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<span class="hljs-comment">//总共就一家</span><br>        <span class="hljs-function">vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt; <span class="hljs-title">state</span><span class="hljs-params">(sz+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>)</span></span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//超过两家</span><br>        state[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<span class="hljs-comment">//用一个state来保存偷不偷当前这一家的最大利益</span><br>        state[<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = nums[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i = <span class="hljs-number">2</span> ; i&lt;= sz ;i++)&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//偷这一家和之前两家的利益以及不偷这一家，偷上一家的最大利益</span><br>            state[i] = <span class="hljs-built_in">max</span>(state[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>],state[i<span class="hljs-number">-2</span>]+nums[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>]);<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> state[sz];<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>120.<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/triangle/">三角形最小路径和</a></strong></p><p>思路：用一个dp[n][n]去模拟从起始节点到当前节点的距离。且当前节点的距离为dp[i][j] &#x3D; min(dp[i-1][j-1],dp[i-1][j]) + triangle[i][j];</p><hr><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">minimumTotal</span><span class="hljs-params">(vector&lt;vector&lt;<span class="hljs-type">int</span>&gt;&gt;&amp; triangle)</span> </span>&#123;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> sz = triangle.<span class="hljs-built_in">size</span>();<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> dp[sz][sz]; <br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i =<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;sz;i++)&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//题目规定每一个triangle的值都不大与10000</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;j&lt;=i;j++)&#123;<br>                    dp[i][j] = <span class="hljs-number">10001</span>;<br>                &#125;<br>            &#125;<br>            dp[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>][<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] = triangle[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>][<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<span class="hljs-comment">//让第一个进入dp</span><br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> temp=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i =<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;sz<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>;i++)&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//循环依次表达出每一个节点数值，</span><br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;j&lt;=i;j++)&#123;<br>                    <span class="hljs-comment">/*for(int k=j;k&lt;=j+1;k++)&#123;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">                        temp = dp[i][j] + triangle[i+1][k];</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">                        if(temp&lt;dp[i+1][k]) dp[i+1][k] = temp;</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">                    &#125;*/</span><br>                    <br>                    <span class="hljs-comment">//这个做法和上上面的循环效果相同。</span><br>                    dp[i][j] = <span class="hljs-built_in">min</span>(dp[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>][j<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>],dp[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>][j]) + triangle[i][j];<br>                &#125;<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-type">int</span> min = dp[sz<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>][<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<span class="hljs-comment">//最后查找最末尾一行的最小值即可。</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i =<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;sz;i++)&#123;<br>                <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(dp[sz<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>][i]&lt;min) min =dp[sz<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>][i];<br>            &#125;<br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> min;<br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><strong>62.<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/unique-paths/">不同路径</a></strong></p><p>![.&#x2F;algorithm](.\algorithm\62. 不同路径 - 力扣（LeetCode）_files\robot_maze.png)</p><p>思路：因为每一次只能够向下或者向右走。所以，可以到达每一个节点的不同路径等于到达该节点上面节点和下面节点的路径数量之和。即dp[i][j] &#x3D; dp[i-1][j]+dp[i][j-1];.</p><p>但是，我们这里要注意start右边和下面应该是1，所以我们将dp[0][1]设置为1，这样就可以保障我们的要求可以得到满足。</p><hr><figure class="highlight c++"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c++"><span class="hljs-keyword">class</span> <span class="hljs-title class_">Solution</span> &#123;<br><span class="hljs-keyword">public</span>:<br>    <span class="hljs-function"><span class="hljs-type">int</span> <span class="hljs-title">uniquePaths</span><span class="hljs-params">(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> m, <span class="hljs-type">int</span> n)</span> </span>&#123;<br>        <span class="hljs-type">int</span> dp[m+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>][n+<span class="hljs-number">1</span>];<span class="hljs-comment">//多开一行设置为0，同时设置dp[0][1]或者dp[1][0]为1。</span><br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i=<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;i&lt;=m;i++)<span class="hljs-comment">//循环设置dp[i][j]为0</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j =<span class="hljs-number">0</span>;j&lt;=n;j++)<br>                dp[i][j] = <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        dp[<span class="hljs-number">0</span>][<span class="hljs-number">1</span>] = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> i =<span class="hljs-number">1</span>;i&lt;=m;i++)&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">//每个节点的数值等于上面的加右面的数值</span><br>            <span class="hljs-keyword">for</span>(<span class="hljs-type">int</span> j = <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;j&lt;=n;j++)&#123;<br>                dp[i][j] = dp[i<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>][j] + dp[i][j<span class="hljs-number">-1</span>];<br>            &#125;<br>        &#125;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">return</span> dp[m][n];<span class="hljs-comment">//返回最终节点的数值即可。</span><br>    &#125;<br>&#125;;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>63.<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/unique-paths-ii/">不同路径Ⅱ</a></p><p>64.<a href="https://leetcode.cn/problems/minimum-path-sum/">最小路径和</a></p><p>这两个题目的做法与62题的做法十分相似。</p><h4 id="总结："><a href="#总结：" class="headerlink" title="总结："></a>总结：</h4>]]></content>
    
    
    
